snippet.title: MY BOYFRIEND REACTS TO ABUSIVE AMBER HEARD STANS || NSFW
snippet.description:
Hey guys, so a lot of people have asked me and my boyfriend to do a video of him reacting to abusive Amber Heard stans tweets, please do not watch if you are easily offended. 

His reactions are his own and are in response to the abuse myself and others receive daily for defending Johnny Depp, an innocent man. 

This video is just a bit of fun, however, his anger is not misplaced as some of the tweets we receive are disgusting. 

Thanks for watching guys! You can find us both on social media.
